article.headline: Drake 70, Wagner 63
article.story: DES MOINES, Iowa (AP) -- Klayton Korver scored 18 points and Chris Bryant added 14 to lead Drake over Wagner 70-63 Thursday. Korver had seven rebounds and Bryant connected on four-of-six from 3-point range as Drake (3-5) handed the Seahawks (1-8) their sixth straight loss. The Bulldogs used a 10-0 run to close out the first half and take a 35-26 lead. Drake began the second half with an 11-3 run and Lonnie Randolph's three-pointer gave the Bulldogs their biggest lead at 46-29 with 16:32 left to play. Matt Vitale led Wagner with 19 points, including a 3-pointer with :10 to play to close the gap 69-63. Korver sank two free throws to secure the win for Drake.
